WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.780 --> 00:00:06.120
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:12.740
Yesterday I told you what is the truth

00:00:14.040 --> 00:00:17.020
and that is what we are seeking today.

00:00:17.420 --> 00:00:20.420
In all our seeking

00:00:23.520 --> 00:00:30.260
we may run after the mirage of money,

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:37.540
of power, of friendship, of

00:00:38.520 --> 00:00:46.100
carnal love but ultimately we have to know, that we are running after

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:52.800
the truth that is the Spirit.

00:00:56.260 --> 00:01:04.040
Yesterday I explained to you how the truth manifests itself

00:01:04.980 --> 00:01:13.040
through your finger-tips and you can find out about any disease or any trouble

00:01:14.260 --> 00:01:21.540
that is within you and without. Only thing you have to know how to work it out.

00:01:26.860 --> 00:01:32.700
When the realization takes place, we have to know

00:01:34.460 --> 00:01:39.980
that a complete integration within take place.

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:50.260
That is your physical, emotional, mental and spiritual being

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:57.340
become completely integrated. For example,

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:05.900
you think, you should start some sort of a work.

00:02:08.480 --> 00:02:13.140
That is what your mind tells you but

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:19.460
your heart tells you, "No, no, no, we should not do it."

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:25.380
Then physical being says, "No, no, no, you're very tired, how can you do it?"

00:02:27.780 --> 00:02:33.300
And the spiritual being can say that, "I just don't know what is to be done."

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:40.200
But when you get your realization,

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:47.040
you become very intense, very positive

00:02:47.980 --> 00:02:54.280
and concentrate your mind very clearly on what is to be done.

00:02:57.020 --> 00:03:02.940
Supposing, you have been doing something very wrong all your life

00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:09.720
and you had no courage to get out of it,

00:03:11.600 --> 00:03:18.560
after realization you become very powerful personality within yourself

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:24.740
and then you do exactly what you have to do

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:33.580
which is physically, mentally, emotionally and spiritually absolutely integrated and is correct.

00:03:34.200 --> 00:03:40.400
So naturally, you become a very righteous person, very righteous person.

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:47.000
The whole value system changes. Today the value system for people

00:03:47.640 --> 00:03:54.480
orients, maybe, from money, from power, from some sort of a

00:03:55.080 --> 00:04:02.700
human consideration. A person may think that, I should do

00:04:04.960 --> 00:04:11.460
this thing because by doing this I'll get lot of money - maybe it's little cheating, doesn't matter.

00:04:13.100 --> 00:04:18.080
Maybe, he would like to do something just to gain

00:04:21.840 --> 00:04:27.800
some sort of a power over other. He may dominate some people

00:04:28.640 --> 00:04:33.640
or he may bear some domination because he has to.

00:04:35.180 --> 00:04:42.120
But after realization you get that power of Absoluteness.

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:51.900
For example, Christ, when He saw Marie Magdalene   being stoned,

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:58.720
He stood before her. Now, Christ

00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:05.000
was an Incarnation of Truth and He had nothing to do with the prostitute,

00:05:06.180 --> 00:05:13.660
has no relationship with her, whatsoever. But He stood before her and asked the people,

00:05:13.900 --> 00:05:19.640
"Those who have not committed any sin, can throw stones at Me."

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:30.180
Such courage and such understanding of righteous behavior

00:05:30.940 --> 00:05:35.080
just starts shining in your character.

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:41.540
Then, you understand what is good in every religion.

00:05:43.060 --> 00:05:49.320
When you start reading Bible after realization, you understand

00:05:50.620 --> 00:05:54.340
where it has gone wrong.

00:05:56.380 --> 00:06:01.800
If you have read Khalil Gibran - he's a very great realized soul -

00:06:02.740 --> 00:06:07.220
and he says about Paul, very clearly,

00:06:07.960 --> 00:06:14.140
"This Paul is a very strange man. I don't know what he's about to say.

00:06:14.740 --> 00:06:20.580
He says something, believes in something, has no relationship with Christ."

00:06:22.340 --> 00:06:29.840
A person like Khalil Gibran could say that, otherwise to say something against Bible,

00:06:30.860 --> 00:06:36.140
was absolutely prohibited. He was thrown out of church, he didn't care.

00:06:36.960 --> 00:06:40.080
I say the same thing about Paul.

00:06:40.980 --> 00:06:45.780
Paul has no place in Bible. He should not have been there at all.

00:06:47.220 --> 00:06:51.100
He was the one, who killed so many people.

00:06:52.100 --> 00:06:58.260
There was a little boy of seventeen years whom he tortured and then he thought

00:06:58.600 --> 00:07:04.000
this is the best way to gain more power to become somebody great

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:12.280
in the Christian community. So he took over and he started writing,

00:07:12.900 --> 00:07:18.580
organizing. He's in the Bible - he has never seen Christ.

00:07:20.500 --> 00:07:27.260
All his writings suggest that he was mad with

00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:34.220
ideas of his own and he put all these ideas on people.

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:43.160
This Paul has created such problems today that Christians are having a big problem solving

00:07:43.920 --> 00:07:51.460
the contradictions made by him. You must be have heard about the Bishop of Durham,

00:07:51.980 --> 00:07:58.520
saying that Paul was correct and there was no Immaculate Conception.

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:05.520
It takes courage to say that Christ's birth was an Immaculate Conception and it was,

00:08:06.220 --> 00:08:10.940
no doubt. Verily, He was the Son of God.

00:08:12.760 --> 00:08:17.080
But to say that, you have to have that courage.

00:08:18.140 --> 00:08:23.580
This Bishop of Durham, just to get some more power, maybe,

00:08:23.780 --> 00:08:28.420
or maybe to get some more Christians converted,

00:08:29.920 --> 00:08:34.500
he must have started this kind of a new ideas.

00:08:35.220 --> 00:08:41.700
So many have been condemning Christ by this kind of authorities.

00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:48.640
And then when he was very much anointed and

00:08:50.840 --> 00:08:56.120
given honor by Archbishop of Canterbury,

00:08:57.600 --> 00:09:03.560
that church was burnt. They couldn't explain

00:09:04.380 --> 00:09:09.600
why the church was burnt and people saw

00:09:11.220 --> 00:09:17.140
the lightning looming over that church for hours together -

00:09:18.160 --> 00:09:21.140
it was a miraculous thing that happened.

00:09:22.020 --> 00:09:29.440
But to people like Bishop of Durham or Archbishop, it was

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:36.140
the Grace of God that the lower part, the floor was not burnt, of the church.

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:44.040
Same way you find in Christianity,

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:49.420
as you have in Hinduism, the same thing.

00:09:52.260 --> 00:09:58.100
They said that there was a big problem in the Parliament

00:09:59.040 --> 00:10:04.880
when the Shankaracharya stood up and said that it is

00:10:05.820 --> 00:10:12.880
a right of a every Hindu to be Brahmin or a non-Brahmin, is written in the Gita.

00:10:16.180 --> 00:10:20.460
And a Member of Parliament came  to Me and asked Me, "Mother, what's the answer to this?"

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:27.300
I said Shankaracharya should know that Gita was written by Vyasa

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:32.300
and Vyasa was a illegitimate child of a fisher-woman.

00:10:33.640 --> 00:10:37.680
How could he write that a Brahmin is born?

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:46.340
The caste system, that is the curse of our country, has come from these so called priests, the brahmins.

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:52.160
They are not Brahmins because those who are born again, those who know the Brahma,

00:10:52.480 --> 00:10:57.020
those who have felt the All-Pervading power of God, are the Brahma.

00:10:57.700 --> 00:11:04.520
Least said about the Islam, then the Sikhs, then all these religions you can find

00:11:04.860 --> 00:11:11.060
that there is so much of twisting of the words

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:14.740
just to suit their own purses and their minds.

00:11:15.940 --> 00:11:23.880
You get over all that and you become powerful to say that it's all wrong - that's not where we have to be.

00:11:26.020 --> 00:11:29.700
Now, so many things are coming out of Vatican

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:35.120
but the Catholics will close their ears - they would not like to listen to all that what is happening.

00:11:35.620 --> 00:11:40.280
Everybody will be exposed, who are doing falsehood.

00:11:40.480 --> 00:11:46.060
The time has come, the judgment time has come - all such people have to  be exposed.

00:11:47.740 --> 00:11:54.740
But the simple people, who love Christ, who love Krishna,

00:11:55.640 --> 00:12:00.540
who loved righteousness, will be saved.

00:12:03.500 --> 00:12:09.600
After realization people also get lots of dynamic

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:13.620
forces within themselves which they never expected to get.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:20.880
First of all, their innocence is awake.

00:12:23.420 --> 00:12:29.140
Whatever innocence they have lost through the stupidity of the society

00:12:29.800 --> 00:12:35.940
or the ideas given by the uh, uh.. enterprising

00:12:37.800 --> 00:12:44.300
film industries or other, we can say, magazines and all kinds of publications -

00:12:45.300 --> 00:12:53.340
all those things drop out. All the conditionings of the mind drop out and he becomes innocent,

00:12:53.980 --> 00:13:01.340
a innocent personality. An innocent personality is a very, very powerful personality.

00:13:01.840 --> 00:13:05.920
As Christ has said, "Thou shalt not have adulterous eyes."

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:10.880
Such a person has a glint in the eye of innocence

00:13:11.240 --> 00:13:17.740
and such person can grow up to such a level that even a little glance of such a person

00:13:17.980 --> 00:13:21.180
can save people from calamities.

00:13:23.020 --> 00:13:27.520
The purity of mind, purity of character,

00:13:28.400 --> 00:13:32.380
all these starts shining in such a personality.

00:13:33.420 --> 00:13:38.600
And such a personality is an auspicious figure.

00:13:39.180 --> 00:13:42.500
Auspiciousness, we have forgotten about.

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:47.500
If an auspicious person enters into the house -

00:13:48.040 --> 00:13:55.220
if somebody's sick that person gets all right, if there's quarrel in the house the quarrel subsides,

00:13:55.720 --> 00:14:02.360
if there's any problem that problem is solved. An auspicious person travelling by a train,

00:14:03.600 --> 00:14:06.880
if there's an accident, nobody dies.

00:14:07.880 --> 00:14:11.900
Auspicious person is the person who is

00:14:12.220 --> 00:14:17.740
constructive and is releasing constructive forces all around him

00:14:19.340 --> 00:14:25.280
of very soothing, peaceful and a very powerful character.

00:14:26.680 --> 00:14:33.060
Such an auspicious personality is to be found in so many realized souls.

00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:42.660
Now the other day, one lady was telling Me that there are many realized souls walking about on this earth - I haven't seen any.

00:14:45.080 --> 00:14:49.240
They might grow their beard, they might wear some sort of a wig,

00:14:49.500 --> 00:14:53.860
they might wear some sort of a dress - that doesn't mean they're realized souls.

00:14:54.340 --> 00:14:59.460
Actually, a realized soul doesn't need to publish or to uh..exhibit

00:14:59.660 --> 00:15:03.620
in any way artificial that he's a realized soul.

00:15:04.400 --> 00:15:11.600
He could be a very ordinary person on the street or he could be a king. He could be

00:15:11.840 --> 00:15:19.560
a, a person just cleaning the hall here and he could be a Prime Minister.

00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:28.620
For such a personality all these things do not matter, whether he lives in comfort,

00:15:29.480 --> 00:15:34.380
he doesn't feel the feeling of comfort, I should say.

00:15:35.180 --> 00:15:39.380
Whether he lives in complete poverty, he doesn't feel it.

00:15:40.220 --> 00:15:44.580
According to the pattern of his life, .

00:15:44.800 --> 00:15:48.920
according to the status of his life, he lives.

00:15:50.020 --> 00:15:54.540
Supposing he's born in a poor family, he lives like a poor man.

00:15:55.360 --> 00:15:58.880
If he's born in a rich family, he lives like a rich man.

00:15:59.280 --> 00:16:05.080
It is not necessary for a rich man to show off uh..that I'm a poor man

00:16:06.620 --> 00:16:09.980
because riches do not touch him.

00:16:11.280 --> 00:16:15.880
They have to be there because he has got it.

00:16:16.520 --> 00:16:19.580
But such a person is extremely generous.

00:16:19.840 --> 00:16:26.820
If he finds that somebody needs the money, he'll give but if he finds that somebody doesn't need the money, he will not give

00:16:27.040 --> 00:16:30.980
and sometimes people are surprised - they think he's miserly.

00:16:31.580 --> 00:16:36.220
Because the sense of discretion is tremendous in an innocent person.

00:16:38.280 --> 00:16:41.960
He develops that sense of discretion so spontaneously -

00:16:42.340 --> 00:16:48.900
as soon as he sees the person, he knows how far to go with that person and how to deal with that person.

00:16:50.120 --> 00:16:53.280
He doesn't have to ask any questions.

00:16:55.940 --> 00:17:03.060
One day some sahaja yogies came to Me in Poona and started telling Me

00:17:03.300 --> 00:17:07.920
about one person that, "Mother, he's a politician, you be very careful with him

00:17:08.120 --> 00:17:14.260
and You, when You're dealing with him, You have to be very much uh.. on Your guard."

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:20.100
I said that's all you have come to tell Me all of you. They said, "That's all." I said now you sit down and I'll tell you.

00:17:20.480 --> 00:17:28.100
I said, I know, this man has eloped with somebody else's wife and this is an illegitimate child he has

00:17:28.280 --> 00:17:34.440
and he's this and he's that, he's that and they were all shocked how Mother came to know about it.

00:17:38.800 --> 00:17:43.040
So there is no need to put any guard - you are guarded all the time.

00:17:43.760 --> 00:17:50.000
The blessings of protection, are all the time with a person, who is a realized soul.

00:17:50.460 --> 00:17:56.820
That's why he's not bothered. He's least bothered about uh..insurances,

00:17:58.500 --> 00:18:05.700
he's least bothered about money, he's least bothered about getting elected -

00:18:10.320 --> 00:18:14.560
he lives in his own world of reality.

00:18:18.400 --> 00:18:23.320
Such a person may suddenly become dynamically artistic -

00:18:24.280 --> 00:18:27.740
he may not have known art at all.

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:35.040
I met one gentleman who came to sahaja yoga, who had lost his job, he had no money, nothing with him,

00:18:35.360 --> 00:18:43.260
so he said, "Mother, I have no money, what am I to do?" I said don't you worry, you take your realization. He got his realization.

00:18:44.500 --> 00:18:52.500
I said why don't you try interior decoration. He said, "What, I don't know timber, I don't know the quality anything, [UNCLEAR- KNOW?] what to do it."

00:18:52.820 --> 00:18:59.500
I said you just see vibrations and work it out. And you'll be amazed, he's now a very good

00:19:00.040 --> 00:19:04.580
interior decorator - he's making good money out of it.

00:19:07.520 --> 00:19:13.040
So many things like that happen to that person. Suddenly, you get your realization,

00:19:14.700 --> 00:19:20.600
you start making poems, poetry - that can happen to anyone of you.

00:19:21.340 --> 00:19:26.540
But these are still, I would say, are temptations - you should not get lost with it.

00:19:27.120 --> 00:19:33.120
Some people can get lots of money, just after realization - it's a temptation.

00:19:34.500 --> 00:19:42.000
Suddenly from somewhere, you might get money but, I would say, it's a temptation - you have to go ahead with it.

00:19:43.340 --> 00:19:46.820
Some people might get a big position suddenly,

00:19:47.420 --> 00:19:55.220
they may land up as something very uh.. great leaders -

00:19:56.580 --> 00:20:03.940
that's also, I think, is a temptation and one should not forget that this is all the Grace of God.

00:20:06.620 --> 00:20:11.920
The people, who are suffering from diseases, get cured. You saw yesterday, how two persons,

00:20:12.140 --> 00:20:17.620
within five minutes, got cured of such horrible diseases - they would have been dead.

00:20:22.200 --> 00:20:27.720
But those who get realization, also get protection from diseases.

00:20:28.320 --> 00:20:33.100
Say, a person suffering from A.I.D.S., will get protection.

00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:37.700
He may not go to the second stage.

00:20:38.860 --> 00:20:43.080
He might live all his life with the first stage, maybe, he might get get cured completely.

00:20:44.700 --> 00:20:52.620
There can be lots of physical benefits he can have. His health will improve, he'll drop down, at least, 10 to 20 years

00:20:54.100 --> 00:20:59.300
and he can do lots of work without getting tired.

00:21:00.440 --> 00:21:07.660
Because you don't feel you're doing any work. Most of the headache is because we think we're doing the work.

00:21:08.640 --> 00:21:11.840
If we can stop thinking that we're doing any work,

00:21:13.760 --> 00:21:18.820
we are not tired. You just do the work, that's all, we don't think about it.

00:21:19.220 --> 00:21:25.300
In England, I find, everybody is [SHRI MATAJI EXHALES - HA]. 'What's the matter?' "I'm tired."

00:21:25.920 --> 00:21:30.640
'What have you done?' "Little cooking, that's all." Because you're thinking you're cooking -

00:21:30.820 --> 00:21:35.280
the cooking was spoilt because of that and now you're tired. [SHRI MATAJI EXHALES - HA]

00:21:38.540 --> 00:21:46.540
But the people who are realized souls, do not think about it. Now for example, there's a beautiful carpet here.

00:21:48.200 --> 00:21:54.300
This doesn't belong to Me - thank God - and I'm looking at it.

00:21:56.120 --> 00:22:03.360
When I look at it, I just see the beauty, the joy that is put in it

00:22:03.840 --> 00:22:09.260
by the artist - I don't think, I just look at it, I witness it.

00:22:10.020 --> 00:22:14.360
I just don't think and the joy that has created this

00:22:14.920 --> 00:22:20.620
completely starts pouring into Me, relieving Me completely.

00:22:23.340 --> 00:22:26.320
To possess something is a headache.

00:22:27.520 --> 00:22:33.020
You possess, say, this carpet, then you must insure it,

00:22:33.280 --> 00:22:36.740
would be worried - I hope it's not getting dirty or this and that.

00:22:39.560 --> 00:22:45.980
To possess some personality, somebody as a husband or a wife, is another, the greater headache

00:22:46.780 --> 00:22:51.800
because all the time you're trying to possess, other person is trying to run away.

00:22:53.820 --> 00:23:01.400
But you stand on your own legs - not to be possessed by anyone nor do you possess anyone.

00:23:03.100 --> 00:23:06.480
You stand in your own glory, enjoying yourself.

00:23:07.620 --> 00:23:13.700
You're not bothered as to who is your husband and that you should possess him.

00:23:13.900 --> 00:23:18.800
"All right, if it's my husband, all right, I can enjoy his company all right.

00:23:19.160 --> 00:23:26.060
But if he doesn't want to enjoy my company, I'm not going to fall at his feet. Let him go ahead.

00:23:30.260 --> 00:23:34.520
Makes no difference to me to my life."

00:23:34.760 --> 00:23:40.260
And you'll be surprised, all such people become very good husband and wives -

00:23:40.480 --> 00:23:43.440
not only that but very good parents.

00:23:43.760 --> 00:23:50.940
We have seen now, in sahaja yoga, so many people are married - they're very happily married people and they have beautiful children too.

00:23:51.440 --> 00:23:55.540
Then you become very good parents because you understand your children

00:23:55.760 --> 00:24:00.560
if they're born realized or not, if they have problems then how to correct the problems,

00:24:00.820 --> 00:24:04.900
how to treat them - you just don't go to doctors for every small little thing.

00:24:09.340 --> 00:24:16.040
This has been already prophecized long, long time back, thousands of years back, in India

00:24:16.900 --> 00:24:22.480
by a very uh.. old astrologer called Bhrigu.

00:24:23.620 --> 00:24:27.200
He's the one who has written Bhrigu samhita,

00:24:27.460 --> 00:24:33.220
which is actually, we should say, he's the one who started astrology.

00:24:35.440 --> 00:24:42.220
He has written that such and such time will come when the Kundalini will rise very easily

00:24:42.440 --> 00:24:46.440
and there will be no need to have any hospitals.

00:24:48.520 --> 00:24:55.520
Is already being described but we do not read anything but something sensational,

00:24:56.740 --> 00:24:59.720
something nonsensical.

00:25:00.480 --> 00:25:06.160
Now, people want to read something sensational, perhaps, we have become the matter.

00:25:06.600 --> 00:25:12.260
When we have become the matter, nothing can stir us but some sort of a shock.

00:25:12.880 --> 00:25:20.980
And that's why, we go about for this kind of literature which is shocking, which we call as sensational.

00:25:23.100 --> 00:25:28.140
A person who is a realized soul, his whole value system changes thoroughly.

00:25:28.640 --> 00:25:35.900
and his whole being becomes such a deep personality that he understands what is

00:25:36.500 --> 00:25:43.440
stupid, what is idiotic, what is wasteful and what is nourishing.

00:25:45.880 --> 00:25:51.700
As if in his brain a new light has come to judge what is good for him.

00:25:55.580 --> 00:26:00.360
Then such a person, suddenly develops, beautiful voice.

00:26:01.980 --> 00:26:05.480
He becomes very compassionate, kind.

00:26:06.660 --> 00:26:14.320
I've seen people who have been all the time abusing each other suddenly become very sweet to each other -

00:26:14.860 --> 00:26:21.480
they give up abusing. They use very gentle, beautiful words.

00:26:22.120 --> 00:26:28.940
They do things to please each other, they try to find out how to make others happy

00:26:31.400 --> 00:26:37.180
Their little, little ways are so sweet.

00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:40.620
I cannot relate all of them to you

00:26:43.060 --> 00:26:49.800
but their one incident I'll tell you that will make you understand

00:26:49.980 --> 00:26:54.820
how these people understand how to make you happy.

00:26:57.200 --> 00:27:04.100
Like we have between ourselves a custom called a rakhi

00:27:04.920 --> 00:27:11.660
in which a brother is to be chosen and you have to tie a, a little

00:27:11.880 --> 00:27:15.580
thread on the wrist of that person.

