00:28:09.260 --> 00:28:12.260
His wife was a clever Indian lady

00:28:13.140 --> 00:28:19.620
so she sent a, that thread in one plate covered with a cloth - that's how we send it -

00:28:20.680 --> 00:28:27.120
to the king and the king asked, "All right, tie that to me."

00:28:27.660 --> 00:28:32.900
