00:28:44.780 --> 00:28:52.440
he fell at the feet of Alexander, he said, "Sir, I'm sorry. Uh.. whatever I've done, please forgive me.

00:28:52.700 --> 00:28:58.660
You are welcome." He took him with him and he put him on his throne. He said, "Let me wash your feet,

00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:05.560
