00:29:05.820 --> 00:29:13.780
This Alexander had no idea what had gone wrong with this king - he thought he's gone mad or what, what is he trying to do?

00:29:14.780 --> 00:29:22.740
So, then he gave lots of clothes and lots of ornaments for his sister and everything and he sent her back to his house.

00:29:25.300 --> 00:29:31.980
